Class ComputerizedExamController

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.gui.ComputerizedExamController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class ComputerizedExamController
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    ComputerizedExamController class handle the start computerized exam screen of the teacher. It shows table of the exams ready to start and allow the teacher to choose the code of the exam.
